{"id": "art-454", "label": "Art. 454", "title": "Art. 454: Dovedirea unor cazuri de revizuire", "slug": "art-454", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_356081915\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1504\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_356081915\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 454:\nDovedirea unor cazuri de revizuire </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1091773151\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1503\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1091773151\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Situa&#355;iile care constituie cazurile de revizuire\nprev&#259;zute la art. 453 alin. (1) lit. b)-d) se dovedesc prin hot&#259;râre\njudec&#259;toreasc&#259; definitiv&#259; prin care instan&#355;a s-a\npronun&#355;at asupra fondului cauzei constatând existen&#355;a falsului sau\nexisten&#355;a faptelor &#351;i s&#259;vâr&#351;irea lor de respectivele\npersoane.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1739495808\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1502\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1739495808\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)În cazurile în care dovada nu poate fi f&#259;cut&#259;\npotrivit alin. (1) datorit&#259; existen&#355;ei unei cauze care împiedic&#259;\npunerea în mi&#351;care sau exercitarea ac&#355;iunii penale, proba cazurilor\nde revizuire prev&#259;zute la art. 453 alin. (1) lit. b)-d) se poate face în\nprocedura de revizuire, prin orice mijloc de prob&#259;.</span></p>"}